{
  "texts": [
    "There are also already efforts to watermark synthetically generated content 40.",
    "However, the extent to which this can be done reliably is an open question 41.",
    "Interactions with the models are therefore often used to constantly expand the space of training data that can be covered.",
    "When dealing with large language models such as GPT, some precautions should therefore be taken about sensitive data.",
    "For example, Samsung engineers have fed confidential data into ChatGPT 42, which poses a significant security risk."
  ]
}